Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's broken promises
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brtj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Apr 1978
Carter's poll rating slip as his broken election promises mount up. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.